title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table within a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that is located within a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data from the table should be successfully exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Insert a table into a grid cell. 2. Insert another table into a different grid cell. 3. Attempt to export the data from the tables.
